data.description: MOTIVATED SELLERS!! Welcome to your new home at 7411 Wheatley Gardens on a large corner lot. Only 20 minutes to downtown Houston and 8 minutes from shopping and dining. Built in 2019 this well-maintained residence boasts 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, a large living room providing ample space for your family. The interior is meticulously kept and offers an open layout for enjoyable family living, a backyard covered patio perfect for entertaining. Don't miss out on this chance to own a beautiful, move-in-ready home. Schedule a viewing today!! LOW TAXES! NEVER FLOODED!
